# Test pack

A [data spreadsheet](/guides/ctc-traders-testing-guide/downloads/NCTS6_Trader_Test_Data_Spreadsheet_13_04_2026.xlsx) that contains master reference data and a spreadsheet representation of the test scenarios
includes all required data elements for key messages.

A [zip file](/guides/ctc-traders-testing-guide/downloads/P6_Example_XML_Payloads_13_04_26.zip) that contains example XML messages - one message for each test scenario

**Note:** The XML files are provided only as examples and may contain optional data. They are not intended to be prescriptive.



